mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "Some Tipes on Teaching Round Dancing", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Vox Saltator: The Square Dancer Speaks Up", "The Changing Square", "Round Dance Abbreviations and Symbols", "Homes for Square Dancing - Square Acres", "Style Series: Which Way Do You Face After - ?", "'Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Caller of the Month: M. P. "Van" Vandever", "Paging the Round Dancers: Sam and Betty Evans", "Current Best Sellers: Record Sales Survey", and "Experimental Lab: U Trail In".
